# VulnTrack - Claude Code Project Prompt

## What this project is

VulnTrack is a full-stack vulnerability tracking platform for security teams. It imports GitHub repositories, scans their dependencies against OSV and NVD databases, auto-generates AI-powered tickets for discovered CVEs, and provides a dashboard with escalation policies and email notifications.

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS, React Query, Recharts |
| Backend | Node.js, Express, TypeScript |
| Database | MySQL 8.0 |
| AI | Anthropic Claude (claude-sonnet-4) via @anthropic-ai/sdk |
| Auth | GitHub OAuth 2.0 + JWT wrapping |
| Background jobs | node-cron |
| Email | Nodemailer (SMTP) |
| Container | Docker + Docker Compose |
| Docs | Swagger UI at /api/docs |

