## Database schema (11 tables)

- **users** - app users (uid, username, email, avatar_url)
- **projects** - repositories (uid, name, git_url, language, default_branch, status)
- **project_contributors** - team members per project
- **project_config** - per-project email flags (email_on_create, email_on_escalate)
- **escalation_config** - per-project escalation rules (days_before_escalate, escalate_email)
- **stable_packages** - known-good package versions
- **vulnerable_packages** - CVE records (cve_id, name, version, severity, cvss_score, fixed_version)
- **project_latest_packages** - current dependencies detected per project
- **tickets** - vulnerability tickets (uid prefixed VLN-*, severity, status, ai_generated flag)
- **ticket_comments** - user annotations on tickets
- Pre-seeded: 10 CVEs across lodash, express, axios, django, flask, log4j, spring, minimist, node-fetch, pyyaml

